---
title: Ratatouille Filo Galette  with Cheesy Radish and Baby Spinach Salad
description: Ratatouille - this delicious summery veggie stew just got even better. It has all the same rich flavours, but now it comes packaged in crisp, golden pastry. This is one of those meals where the vegetables really shine - you won’t be missing your staple meat and three veg when this is on the table!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67c10cf860686822766eb53b-dcb8e3ef.jpeg
